interpretation:
RETURN TO THIS IF WE CARE: This feature detects a very specific Yelp review opening formula:

  [I/We] + [visited/ate at/dined at] + [this/the] + [descriptive?] + [cuisine] + restaurant + [time phrase] + [positive reaction]

  Required:
  - First person: "I" or "We"
  - Verbs: "visited", "ate at", "dined at" (NOT "went to", "tried")
  - Article: "this" or "the" (NOT "a")
  - Cuisine type: Mexican, Italian, Chinese, etc.

  Forbidden:
  - Third person subjects
  - "yesterday" or "last night" as time phrase
  - Evaluative adjectives before cuisine (amazing, excellent)
  - Indefinite article "a"
